      </section>

      <div class="seam"><img src="/cag-header-logo-160.webp" width="54" height="54" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></div>

      <!-- 10 · RESERVE / FORM -->
      <section id="reserve" class="final-cta">
        <h2 class="cag-h2">Reserve your African Grey eggs — or a weaned chick</h2>
        <p>Tell us what you're after and how you'd like to receive it, and we'll reply within 24 hours with honest availability — including "not right now" if that's the true answer. A $200 deposit reserves a clutch or a bird once we've confirmed the match.</p>
        <form class="cta-form" name="egg-inquiry" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
