          </label>
          <label for="egg-msg">Tell us about your setup <span class="opt">(optional)</span><textarea id="egg-msg" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Do you run an incubator? First bird? Which state are you shipping to?"></textarea></label>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-clay">Start my inquiry</button>
